## Why torch.profiler

This run may execute in a Modal sandbox, which hides `/proc/driver/nvidia/`. `nsys` cannot sync GPU clocks without that file. `torch.profiler` uses CUPTI's Callback API and produces per-kernel timing, operator breakdown, and memory ops in that environment.

